content:
To rename Case Feed actions and feed filters:

Available in: Salesforce Classic (Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions)

Required user permissions:
Customize Application or View Setup and Configuration

1. From Setup, enter Rename Tabs and Labels.
2. Click Edit next to Cases.
3. Find the label you want to change.
4. Type the new name for the label.
5. If it starts with a vowel sound, check Starts with vowel sound.
6. Click Save.

Rename actions and feed filters to match your company's terms.
title: Renaming Case Feed Actions and Filters in Service Cloud
